para_trans: Hon'ble Minister of State for Government
Government Decision, No.Shaniva-1525 / Q. No.32 / Niwas-2
Reference: - General Administration Department, Government Decision, No.Shaniva-1524 / Q.No.312 / Residence-2 dated 23rd December 2024
Mr. Indranil Anita Manohar Naik, Hon'ble Minister of State at "Suniti-09," Churchgate, Mumbai.
The decision to allot the government accommodation, which was taken under the relevant government decision, has now been cancelled.
Shri Indranil Anita Manohar Naik, Hon'ble Minister of State for Home Affairs to allot Government Residence Suniti-6 at Churchgate instead of Government Residence Suniti-09 at Churchgate.
The decision has been taken by the government.
The residence allotted to the Hon'ble Minister of State shall be compulsorily vacated within a period of fifteen days after his discharge from office.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
